nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.environment.constants

Class GenericConstantLoader.Builder<U>

  • nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.environment.constants.GenericConstantLoader.Builder<U>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentLoaderBuilder<TComponentLoader>
    Enclosing class:
    GenericConstantLoader<T>

    public static class GenericConstantLoader.Builder<U>
implements ComponentLoaderBuilder<TComponentLoader>

    A custom interface ComponentLoaderBuilder implementation for building a class GenericConstantLoader instance.

    The builder allows for a collection of constants (as strings) to be specified, which will be parsed into the type specified as a type parameter.

    See Also:
    interface ComponentLoaderBuilder, class GenericConstantLoader
